    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "resolved": "true",
    "text": "I'd flip Olivia and Bianca \u2014 Bianca has been crushing the ball in BP and we need her driving in runs from the four hole."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
