    "parent_block_id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467bc",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f3",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Good call Raymond. Locking Maya at leadoff since she's seeing the ball well and can bunt for a hit if they play her deep."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "u3b91d2c7f45a8e6019bd47c2a1e3f508",
