    "parent_block_id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467c5",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Their cleanup hitter went oppo twice last game, so let's not over-shift the left side or she'll just slap it the other way."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
    "created_time": "2026-02-09T11:20:49+00:00",
    "id": "97bdf5996f35321b274d51b02f29ad4c",
    "parent_block_id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467c6",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f4",
    "resolved": "true",
    "text": "Charted it \u2014 she throws the rise on 1-2 and 0-2 almost every time. We'll lay off the high stuff with two strikes."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "u9a4c1e8b6d27f3094a51c0e7b8d24631",
    "created_time": "2026-02-11T10:27:51+00:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447753",
    "parent_block_id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467cf",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Coach, can we add ten minutes of conditioning at the end of Tuesday practice? A few of the girls gassed late last weekend."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
    "created_time": "2026-02-12T09:30:39+00:00",
    "id": "cea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae185447754",
    "parent_block_id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467d0",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f5",
    "resolved": "true",
    "text": "Will do. I'll bring three buckets so we can run two bunt stations at once and keep the reps moving."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "u3b91d2c7f45a8e6019bd47c2a1e3f508",
    "created_time": "2026-03-27T11:32:59+00:00",
    "id": "9eb2611104017c3bb5215d8244583b02",
    "parent_block_id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467d9",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f6",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Kayla's footwork on the double-play feed is getting cleaner. Let's give her ten extra turns at second this week."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
