    "parent_block_id": "bea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854467e3",
    "parent_page_id": "pea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854464f7",
    "resolved": "false",
    "text": "Priya's dad here \u2014 she's good to start game one, but she pitched a long bullpen Thursday so let's watch her count early."
  },
  {
    "author_id": "uea790e4a248dab6ac4b6ae1854463c7",
